{
  "texts": [
    "40 Sample sizes varied across studies, ranging from eight to 5,701 participants.",
    "All studies stated participants' gender except one.",
    "36 Only three studies had a larger proportion of female participants.",
    "38, 39, 45 The volunteer-based nature of participant recruitment meant selection and non-response bias was present.",
    "Findings could not be generalised to the wider surgical trainee population as participants were self-motivated and self-aware."
  ]
}